text: Marko Tarabochia (born 28 November 1988) is a Croatian-born Bosnian handball player for RK Metalurg Skopje and the Bosnian national team.EHF profile ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina male handball players Category:Wisła Płock (handball) players
